\b Synapse – Architecture & Technical Overview\b0\par
\par
\b 1. Purpose & Vision\b0\par
Synapse helps technicians identify spare parts (via text or images), verify stock and warranty, and act quickly. It emphasizes speed, clarity, and trust – the “Five‑Minute Fix”.\par
\par
\b 2. Tech Stack\b0\par
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript, Vite, React Router, TanStack Query\par
- UI: Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Radix, Lucide icons\par
- Analytics: @vercel/analytics\par
- Backend: Node, Express, dotenv\par
- AI: Google Gemini 1.5 Pro (text+vision) via @google/generative-ai\par
- Dev: ESLint, Nodemon\par
\par
\b 3. System Architecture\b0\par
User (Web/Teams) -> React (Vite) -> /api -> Express (8787) -> Gemini 1.5 Pro\par
Camera/File -> base64 -> /api/ask (vision)\par
\par
\b 3.1 Frontend Modules\b0\par
- src/components/spares-chat.tsx: Chat, file, camera, disambiguation\par
- src/components/ui/camera-capture.tsx: getUserMedia capture flow\par
- src/components/synapse-loading.tsx: stepwise loading\par
- src/components/synapse-result-card.tsx: part/inventory/warranty\par
- src/pages/Index.tsx: Landing + demo\par
- src/pages/TeamsConfig.tsx: Teams tab configuration\par
\par
\b 3.2 Backend Modules\b0\par
- server/index.js\par
  - GET /api/health\par
  - POST /api/ask (text|image base64) -> Gemini -> { text }\par
\par
\b 3.3 Configuration\b0\par
- .env: GEMINI_API_KEY, PORT\par
- Vite proxy /api -> 8787\par
- .gitignore excludes .env\par
\par
\b 4. Data & Security\b0\par
- Secrets only on server; CORS hardened in prod\par
\par
\b 5. UX & Accessibility\b0\par
- Deep slate + cyan; IBM Plex Sans; WCAG AA\par
- Low stock lozenge; camera living input\par
\par
\b 6. Microsoft Teams Integration\b0\par
- Tab App: teams/manifest.json, /teams-config\par
- Future Bot: Azure Bot Service + Bot Framework\par
\par
\b 7. Local Development\b0\par
npm install\par
npm run server:start\par
npm run dev\par
\par
\b 8. Deployment\b0\par
- Frontend (Vercel/Netlify/Azure Static)\par
- Backend (Render/Railway/Azure App Service)\par
- Teams: update manifest URLs, package, upload\par
\par
\b 9. Roadmap\b0\par
- RAG + vector DB; vision embeddings; Teams bot/extensions\par
\par
\b 10. API Contract\b0\par
POST /api/ask\par
Request: messages[], optional image dataURL\par
Response: { text }\par
}
